Class OneEvalResult

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.epoch.evals.OneEvalResult

  • public class OneEvalResult
extends Object
    Holds the result of the evaluation of a response by a single evaluator.

        Whether this response can only be graded by human intervention.

      • calcScore

        Score calculated from this response by this evaluator. Used only by a few particular evaluators. Negative if not used.
